flowchart TD
  P{"--inproc-preconditioner<br/>solve_one L233"} --> MT["mean_tangent<br/>build_preconditioner_factors L313/L204<br/>block-diag D_k + Bphi diag(gamma_mean) BphiT, per-harmonic SuperLU"]
